    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Joint Recall Demo</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在 Joint Recall Demo 中，你和你的朋友可以一起体验游戏，玩教程并探索在线多人模式中的多个关键地点。通过语音聊天合作，克服障碍、解决难题并发现游戏世界中的秘密。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148150/extras/027b1ba49666eac7acb9d74c9eb4eba2.poster.avif?t=1727700543\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148150/extras/027b1ba49666eac7acb9d74c9eb4eba2.webm?t=1727700543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148150/extras/027b1ba49666eac7acb9d74c9eb4eba2.mp4?t=1727700543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Co-op horror extraction shooter.</strong> <br>探索废弃的建筑，听朋友被怪物窒息的尖叫。深入未知领域，在黑暗中射击，派遣队友作为诱饵，寻找补给，并感受成功撤离的肾上腺素。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148150/extras/db68926a7275b6304d0e5c19101cffe4.poster.avif?t=1727700543\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148150/extras/db68926a7275b6304d0e5c19101cffe4.webm?t=1727700543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148150/extras/db68926a7275b6304d0e5c19101cffe4.mp4?t=1727700543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  <br><strong>团队合作的重要性</strong>  <br>在你和你的朋友们穿越危险的环境时，合作是至关重要的，使用语音聊天保持联系并协调你们的行动。无论是远程指挥还是共同面对挑战，沟通都能确保生存。利用无线电和陷阱等工具来击败威胁，确保你的团队安全。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148150/extras/07471fe6a1f5a1ecb83264a7efcf8cef.poster.avif?t=1727700543\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148150/extras/07471fe6a1f5a1ecb83264a7efcf8cef.webm?t=1727700543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148150/extras/07471fe6a1f5a1ecb83264a7efcf8cef.mp4?t=1727700543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  <br><strong>掠夺的力量</strong>  <br>搜集有价值的物品，将你的发现安全撤离，并将它们转化为强大的升级，提升你角色的能力。根据你的游戏风格自定义和升级装备，出售多余的物品获取利润，并在面对新的挑战时扩展你的武器库。你收集的每一件物品都可能成为你在危险的《Joint Recall》世界中变得更强、更聪明、更富有的关键。</p>",
